I. How to build primesieve (Windows, Linux, Mac OS X)
=====================================================

  Prerequisites
  -------------
  Since version 3.5 the primesieve GUI application requires a compiler
  that supports OpenMP 3.0 or later (2008). The Qt SDK includes a
  recent version of g++ which works fine.

  1. Download and install the Qt SDK from:
     http://qt.nokia.com/downloads

  2. Launch the primesieve.pro project file with the Qt-Creator IDE
     and have a look at Qt-Creator-build-settings.png for the
     compilation steps.

II. Remarks
===========

  primesieve has been developed with Qt 4.7, if it does not compile
  with future releases of Qt old Qt4 builds can be retrieved from:
  ftp://ftp.trolltech.com/qt/source/
